---
By: Thomas a Kempis
Locus:
  Page: 253
  Verse: 4
Tags:
  - Humility
---
Do not consider yourself to have madeany spiritual progress, unless
youaccount yourself the least of allmen. ...Resolve to do the will of
othersrather than your own. Always choose topossess less rather than more.
Alwaystake the lowest plane, and regardyourself as less than others.
